collections.name: C. 40 Days ( NFT Certificate Of Authenticity)
collections.description:
This exclusive release offers a dynamic experience, blending both the physical and digital realms. "C. 40 Days" comes with its physical (tangible) masterpiece and a state-notarized certificate of authenticity sealed with wax by the signet ring of The HeART Hatter.

This art has been crafted with the intention of shifting the way you experience art. This NFT secures the connection between the tangible art and its digital counterpart.

"C. 40 Days" NFT is a unique digital asset that encapsulates Craig's reflections on his 40-day journey with The HeART Hatter, intricately intertwined with Craig's personal journey, existing alongside the painting. Accompanied by soul-stirring original music composed by Craig and Digital Rose, the music elevates the narrative, bringing the painting to life in a deeply immersive and profound way.

This NFT drop is designed not only to connect the physical and digital worlds but also to ensure security and traceability. By using the NFT as a certificate of authenticity, Logan-Miles expresses the desire that both the tangible artwork and its digital counterparts remain linked. This approach secures the integrity of the piece, making it traceable and providing peace of mind to the buyer.

If "C. 40 Days" tangible artwork is purchased, the purchaser agrees that the NFT must be transferred alongside if sold, and if "C. 40 Days" NFT is sold, the tangible artwork will be included in the agreement and shipped accordingly to the agreement between the parties—respecting that the full experience stays together as intended.

While not guaranteed, it is requested that the two remain together, preserving the integrity of both the physical and digital elements.

It is important to note that while the NFT includes the digital asset, the buyer will not receive full rights to the music or lyrics. This is more than an NFT drop or a work of art—it is a world-changing experience that touches on the eternal truths of life, inviting those who acquire it to witness the powerful puzzle that "sits on the table."

NOT FOR EVERYONE:

1st Purchaser of "C. 40 Days" will receive The HeART Hatter C. 40 Days Solodome Art Chair: (Surprise!)

(1/1)
(Patented Therapeutic Sound Chair)
(Color Interior) - Black Leather
(Color Exterior) - White w. HeART Hatter Art

"This chair is like sitting in the world’s best sound booth, one has never heard until they do!! The comfort and audio take people away from the world and put you into a whole different realm! It allows the mind to really feel, to really see the angles of a painting one may never get to experience! A real POWERFUL and EMOTIONAL ADVENTURE!"

collections.name: Phases of Return
collections.description: Do you ever feel the presence of the Moon? Across each of the 174 unique works, “Phases of Return” hides lunar cycles in plain sight. Waxing, waning, eclipsing—each composition conceals the shifting moon in the curves of profiles and hats, the split of light and shadow, the quiet geometry of the unseen. Faces meet and part like celestial bodies crossing in orbit, caught between recognition and mystery. Drawing from Chae Tongyull’s medieval series as a foundation, this Orangehare in-house production evokes an older, more medieval understanding of the self and the other. Can you spot the lunar cycle in each piece? Designed and brought to life through Orangehare’s in-house production process.
